  "instructions": [
    "Combine tomato puree and tempering chocolate in a small bowl.",
    "Mix in Greek yogurt until smooth.",
    "Add chopped spinach and crumbled feta cheese. Mix well.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, honey, and lemon juice to taste.",
    "Place the pandan leaf wrap on a flat surface and spread the mixture evenly down the center of the wrap.",
    "Add chopped fresh cilantro on top of the mixture.",
    "Fold the bottom half of the wrap up over the mixture, then fold in the sides and roll the wrap up tightly.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
